cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is about improving the performance of transformer networks in natural language processing tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses regularization techniques and pruning, which are common topics in machine learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) the second most likely category. The paper also mentions language understanding benchmarks, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper discusses summarization and question answering, which are related to computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE), respectively.
